                    </p>
                </div>
                
                

                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-12 mt-4 mt-lg-0 ms-auto">
                   

                    <p class="copyright-text mt-lg-5 mt-4">Copyright Â© 2024 Freelancing Center. All rights reserved.
